      "content": "look i get it, but i'm literally just sitting on my couch right now. i'm not even sweating or anything, it's just that weird heavy feeling. if i take a couple of extra strength antacids and a baby aspirin, shouldn't that cover the bases for both the indigestion and any potential heart stuff? it seems way more logical than sitting in an emergency room for 6 hours for nothing. just give me a straight answer, is that a safe way to handle it for tonight?",
